[I] A library for accessing DVD drives

[T] Libdvdread lets application developers access DVD hardware nicely, and
[T] uses libdl to probe for libcss at runtime, decrypting encrypted blocks
[T] if found.

[U] https://dvdnav.mplayerhq.hu

